Commercial Application Overview

The product model underpins all the business processes used in the Auto line of business. This line of business offers two products namely Multi Auto and Commercial Auto.

Multi Auto Product Model
The Multi Auto product is a multi-instance product model that lets users create quotes for multiple vehicles driven by multiple drivers.
Commercial Auto Product Model
The Commercial Auto product is a single-instance product model that lets businesses create quotes for multiple vehicles from a single location.
